1. Copy the api/_site.py template to api/site.py and fill in the appropriate values

    serverHttpIp    : the IP of the server where the site runs (www.recipicon.com)
    serverSmtp      : the host name of the SMTP server
    serverPort      : SMTP TLS port
    serverFromEmail : from email address
    serverFromName  : from name
    serverPass      : SMTP server pass